Package: config-nginx-404-portal
Architecture: all
Depends: nginx
Description: Provides locations/404-portal for nginx
 Provides universal 404 error_page configuration, which proxies all 404 to any.yandex.ru
 Just add "include locations/404-portal;" to your config to use this. 

